Summary: Strange lights all the same in the sky over Gulf of Mexico
trends: There have been 20 other sightings in Venice
There was one other sighting in Venice on or around November 3rd 2011
divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband and I were walking on the beach and looking South from Venice Island when we noticed some lights in the sky over the Gulf of Mexico. We saw one, then two, then three and they all blinked out at once. Then we saw three again much further to the west. They also blinked out at the same time. Then we saw one light appear, then two, three, four, five, six and seven until there were seven in a row in the sky. They all disappeared at the same time. My husband said we just saw a UFO! We were very excited!
